  "title": "Drafter",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for general drafting work including the detailing of architectural, civil and structural and other related drawings from design drafts.</li>\n  <li>Production of drawings on CAD and BIM Revit model for C&amp;S works.</li>\n  <li>Prepare and update 3D BIM model for submissions.</li>\n  <li>Prepare draft outline and detailed drawings to the appropriate scale for planning submissions and construction purposes.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with project team and external stakeholders on tender and construction drawings.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Diploma or Degree in Architecture, Civil Engineering or other relevant disciplines.</li>\n  <li>At least 3 years’ relevant experience in design coordination, preferably on different scales of projects in construction industry.</li>\n  <li>Good knowledge of software such as Revit, AutoCAD.</li>\n  <li>Good planning skills in managing modelling and drafting works.</li>\n  <li>Excellent team player, good interpersonal skills and a “can-do” attitude.</li>\n  <li>Ability to multi-task in a fast paced and dynamic environment.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>Suitable candidates are encouraged to apply this position via Apply Now button or email to <u><strong>Career@kah.com.sg</strong></u></p>\n<p><em>Only shortlisted applicants will be notified.</em></p>",
